<p>Fortune! Prosperity! {<foreign>meykkīrtti</foreign>} This is the twenty fourth year of Śrī Vīrājarājakesarivarman who has become <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>ākiya</foreign></supplied> Śrī Rājarājatēvar. Mahādeva of the Lord <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>īśvarattu</foreign></supplied> <supplied reason="subaudible">of</supplied> Pakaiviṭai in Paḻuvūr, the Lord <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>uṭaiya</foreign></supplied> of the sacred name <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>tirunāmam</foreign></supplied> called Paḻuvūr Nakkar <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></p></div>

